      <h1>Why Employee Health Insurance Costs Keep Rising (And What You Can Do About It)</h1>
      <p class="blog-subtitle">Healthcare costs have increased 47% in the last decade while wages grew just 22%. Here's why this trend continues—and how smart employers are fighting back.</p>
