        <h2>The Bottom Line: Stop Accepting Rising Costs</h2>
        
        <p>Healthcare costs don't have to be an uncontrollable expense that eats away at your profits year after year. While you can't control hospital consolidation or specialty drug prices, you can control how your company approaches employee healthcare benefits.</p>
        
